com.ibm.team.enterprise.scd.common.api

Interface IScanResultAPI


  • public interface IScanResultAPI
    The IScanResultAPI represents the result of a source code data scan.

    The IScanResultAPI includes methods to examine the status, state, and other information of a scan result.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String getLabel()
      Returns the label of this scan result.
      long getScanFinishTime()
      Returns the time the scan was completed.
      java.io.InputStream getScanLog()
      Returns the contents of the scan log.
      long getScanStartTime()
      Returns the time the scan was started.
      IScanSummary getScanSummary()
      Returns the summary of the scan.
      ScanState getState()
      Returns the current state of the scan.
      ScanStatus getStatus()
      Returns the current status of the scan.

    • Method Detail

      • getLabel

        java.lang.String getLabel()
        Returns the label of this scan result.
        Returns:
        the literal string label which will be empty if the scan has not started.

      • getStatus

        ScanStatus getStatus()
        Returns the current status of the scan.
        Returns:
        one of the followings: ScanStatus.OK, ScanStatus.WARNING, ScanStatus.ERROR.

      • getState

        ScanState getState()
        Returns the current state of the scan.
        Returns:
        one of the followings: ScanState.NOT_STARTED, ScanState.SCANNING, ScanState.INDEXING, ScanState.COMPLETED, ScanState.CANCELLED.

      • getScanFinishTime

        long getScanFinishTime()
        Returns the time the scan was completed.
        Returns:
        the time the scan was completed in milliseconds.

      • getScanStartTime

        long getScanStartTime()
        Returns the time the scan was started.
        Returns:
        the time the scan was started in milliseconds.

      • getScanLog

        java.io.InputStream getScanLog()
        Returns the contents of the scan log.
        Returns:
        the contents of the scan log.

      • getScanSummary

        IScanSummary getScanSummary()
        Returns the summary of the scan.
        Returns:
        the IScanSummary that includes the summary of the scan.
